wiki.summary: “OKI DOKI” is a song by Colombian singer KAROL G, released for her album “Mañana Será Bonito (Bichota Season). The song narrates a message of female empowerment and the importance of recognizing one's own self-esteem in relationships. The song encourages listeners to take charge of their lives and not be afraid to free themselves from toxic or unsatisfying associations. Read more on Last.fm.
